  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAfter updating to `v1.0.5`, many users have experience this error which prevents BN startup:\r\n\r\n```\r\nCRIT Failed to start beacon node             reason: Slasher open error: BincodeError(Io(Kind(UnexpectedEof)))\r\n``` \r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/releases/tag/v1.0.5\r\n\r\n## Work-around\r\n\r\nYou can one of two things to resolve this temporarily:\r\n\r\n1. Delete the `~/.lighthouse/mainnet/beacon/slasher_db` directory, then restart the BN.\r\n1. Omit the `--slasher` flag.\r\n\r\n## Additional Info\r\n\r\nI'm not sure if this is directly related to `v1.0.5` or if it's just the first reboot many have done since the slasher db wrapped-around. This requires more investigation. \r\n",
